@startuml config-snapshot-lifecycle
title Configuration Snapshot Lifecycle

[*] --> Draft : Proposed Change

Draft --> PendingApproval : Submitted for Umbrella Review
PendingApproval --> Approved : Governance Approval Received
PendingApproval --> Rejected : Change Denied

Approved --> Active : Replaced current runtime config
Active --> Rollback : Previous version restored

Active --> Archived : Version Superseded
@enduml
